const uint16 SPACE_DATA_MAPPING_KEY_CLIENT_ONLY = 2

This constant is the index for SpaceData concerning what geometry data is mapped into the space.

It only influences the client. The server will not load this geometry.

const uint16 SPACE_DATA_MAPPING_KEY_CLIENT_SERVER = 1

This constant is the index for SpaceData concerning what geometry data is mapped into the space.

It influences both the client and the server.
